
Calendar::Simple
----------------

NAME

  Calendar::Simple

DESCRIPTION

  This is a very simple module that models a calendar month.

INSTALLATION

  To install this module type the following:

       perl Makefile.PL
       make
       make test
       make install


DEPENDENCIES

  This module has no external dependencies.

